{"tid":254789,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"【名家搶先睇】中外資金對港股卻步原因（El.）","createTime":"2017-05-23T12:34:15.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-26T07:45:46.000Z","uid":17738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"d506223dd5ac42344d7da61e8a6581edb597b402","tid":254789,"uid":17738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-23T12:34:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.appledaily.com.hk/images/e-paper/20170523/large/1495537566_9740.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.appledaily.com.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170523%2Flarge%2F1495537566_9740.jpg&h=f80bd2f0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n先係中金出報告羅列66隻本港疑似老千股，再來有David Webb於個人網站上載「50隻不能持有的港股」關係圖，加上沽空機構狙擊個別科技股，外人唔知仲以為港股地雷處處，十面埋「伏」，不宜沾手。<br />\n<br />\n港股淪為大戶抽水樂園日久，本港股民對老千股同莊家股早有提防，不過原來內地投資者亦被本地老千股嚇窒。深港通開車前，市場一度熱切憧憬本地細價股獲北水青睞，但筆者通車前曾經同一名與內地投資者相熟嘅本地基金經理傾過，佢話內地人對本港莊家股嘅配股、供股、合股等搵笨招數已有所聞，因此連帶對透過深港通參與本港細價股亦存在戒心。<br />\n<br />\n市場之前擔心港股A股化會拖低港股質素，但諷刺在今時今日，A股化並非中外投資者對港股扣分嘅主因。監管當局規管不力、莊家毫無節制抽水，人人都抱住自己搵錢為上你死你事嘅心態，造成妖股橫行嘅局面，先係外界對港股卻步嘅元兇。<br />\n<br />\n港人自己唔爭氣斷送國際金融中心聲譽就固然，不過諗深一層，香港搵錢機會愈見罕有，金融或相關行業都不復當年勇，大概亦係莊家及相關人等為搵錢不惜放棄底線嘅原因。但無論因果關係如何，情況長此下去並進一步惡化，港股只會更難吸納中外資金流入，落入邊緣化困局。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=56732409&amp;category_guid=7015342&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20170523\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D56732409%26category_guid%3D7015342%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20170523&d=CUR0kzXGIm1HC%2F%2BZBX5zt%2B9M5Ue6CDmcYDZznX2R1Ws%3D&h=00286f29\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D56732409%26category_guid%3D7015342%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20170523&h=04ed74a2\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=56732409&amp;category_guid=7015342&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20170523</a>"},{"pid":"304d0752ce7cb430731ab0dacb0e8ff6727fd432","tid":254789,"uid":30169,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-24T08:13:31.000Z","msg":"快D玩爛佢"},{"pid":"9d21e2088e9dd33c8cb12e8e5f4d079267f835cf","tid":254789,"uid":56698,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-24T09:12:24.000Z","msg":"玩爛佢就收皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0b8a1c86e3521afe4c50b4a1880cae9712025644","tid":254789,"uid":33263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-26T07:44:22.000Z","msg":"根本係抵死，成交一千億都沒"},{"pid":"7fac8a806c60179a7ab52e13284c7857cce9006a","tid":254789,"uid":5537,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-26T07:45:45.000Z","msg":"玩爛左，除左700 其餘都無咩好買<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6244ca2c6edda02a76031c82486cf8d022e0d523","tid":254789,"uid":522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-26T07:45:46.000Z","msg":"香港人成日都自作孽"}]}